VL  - 24
IS  - 2
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - An investigation on determinants of effective staff work showed that stress in the relationship between the staff officer and the superior constitutes an important moderator variable. When stress with boss was high, experience correlated positively but intelligence correlated negatively with performance evaluations. Intelligence was uncorrelated with performance when the individual reported relatively low stress with his boss.
AB  - An investigation on determinants of effective staff work showed that stress in the relationship between the staff officer and the superior constitutes an important moderator variable. When stress with boss was high, experience correlated positively but intelligence correlated negatively with performance evaluations. Intelligence was uncorrelated with performance when the individual reported relatively low stress with his boss.
